data.description: Discover the allure of suburban serenity in the welcoming community of Little Elm. This inviting home boasts a spacious open floor plan with an eat-in kitchen that includes gleaming SS appliances, perfect for the home chef. The airy vaulted ceilings enhance the sense of space. Entertaining is a delight with a formal dining area and a cozy living room complete with a charming fireplace, setting the stage for memorable evenings. Retreat to the master suite where relaxation awaits in the garden tub, with a separate shower for added convenience. A dedicated laundry room offers practicality and organization. Step outside to the fenced backyard, an ideal canvas for your outdoor paradise. Embrace the opportunity to live in a growing city that promises a blend of tranquility and accessibility, making this home a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
